history.content:
Hello students!

Starting this week until September 16, 2020, Cindy Conners will be offering virtual office hours to replace in-person walk-in office hours. They will take place Monday-Friday via Zoom between 3 - 4pm PST. She will be answering all your CS Enrollment questions on a first-come first-serve basis. We look forward to seeing you there!

You may also email your question to cs-enrollments@cs.Berkeley.edu. Please be sure to include your SID number in the message.

Zoom details:

  • Join meeting: https://berkeley.zoom.us/j/97736717263
  • Meeting ID: 977 3671 7263

For more information visit: https://eecs.berkeley.edu/resources/undergrads/cs/advising/enrollment-drop-in.

Stay safe everyone!
